dcterms:description: The RST-DT Treebank contains 385 documents of the Wall Street Journal corpus, annotated with complete discourse trees according to the RST discourse theory and segmented into Elementary Discourse Units (EDUs) by human annotators.
dcterms:title: RST-DT Treebank

dcterms:description: The Yelp’13 Dataset is a review dataset published as part of the 2013 Yelp Dataset Challenge, containing predominantly restaurant reviews alongside a 5-point star rating, pre-segmented into EDUs.
dcterms:title: Yelp’13 Dataset
